<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reimposta password Orchidea</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0a0a0f;color:#e0e0e0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <div style="max-width:560px;margin:2rem auto;background:#13131f;border:1px solid rgba(157,0,255,0.3);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;">
    <div style="padding:2rem;">
      <h1 style="margin:0 0 1.5rem;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:900;color:#9d00ff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#9d00ff,#ff00e4);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;">
        🌸 Orchidea
      </h1>
      <p style="margin:0 0 0.5rem;color:#e0e0e0;font-size:1rem;">
        Ciao <strong><%= nome %></strong>,
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0.8rem 0 1.5rem;color:#b0b0b0;line-height:1.7;font-size:0.95rem;">
        Hai richiesto di reimpostare la password del tuo account Orchidea.<br>
        Clicca il pulsante qui sotto per scegliere una nuova password.
      </p>
      <a href="<%= link %>"
         style="display:inline-block;padding:0.8rem 2rem;background:#9d00ff;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;">
        Reimposta password &rarr;
      </a>
      <p style="margin:1.5rem 0 0;color:#666;font-size:0.85rem;">
        Il link scade in <strong style="color:#e0e0e0;">1 ora</strong>. Se non hai richiesto questo reset, ignora questa email.
      </p>
      <hr style="margin:2rem 0;border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
      <p style="margin:0;color:#555;font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.6;">
        Orchidea &middot; Via U. Maddalena 40, Rottanova (VE) 30014
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
